article_title: What's the Deal: Commercial Property Transactions in the New York Area
article_text:
Manhattan Flatiron District Tower Attracts Retail Interest

Renovations and increased foot traffic on Broadway has an international retailer interested in a Flatiron District tower, building managers said.

The retailer is in negotiations to lease about 20,000 square feet on two floors of the 20-story commercial building at 915 Broadway, according to ABS Partners Real Estate LLC, which manages the property. The real-estate firm...
